  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Increase one ability score of your choice by 1, to a maximum of 30.</p><p><strong>Improve Fate.</strong> When you or another creature within 60 feet of you succeeds on or fails a D20 Test, you can roll 2d4 and apply the total rolled as a bonus or penalty to the d20 roll. Once you use this benefit, you can't use it again until you roll Initiative or finish a Short or Long Rest.</p><section id=\"secret-zl5SPZXJtl1mEKOl\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Improve Fate</strong> activity includes a roll and automatically restores a use after a Short or Long Rest. It does not automatically refresh after you roll Initiative though.</p></section>",
